#: 21337012-0-3190
msgctxt "21337012-0-3190"
msgid ""
"By Curator Umutha of the House of Orsimer Glories\n"
"\n"
"Here in Orsinium's museum of Orcish history, we are proud to display arms "
"and armor created in the style of our ancient ancestors! Feel free to handle "
"the items labeled \"\"reproduction,\"\" but please admire the original "
"relics in the display cases with your eyes only. \n"
"\n"
"SWORDS\n"
"\n"
"An Ancient Orc's sword looks like a slim single-edged axe-blade attached at "
"two points to a long tang, with a slight curve just below the point. The "
"entire weapon is ornamented with interwoven geometric patterns to create an "
"object of breathtaking beauty."
msgstr ""

#: 51188213-0-3190
msgctxt "51188213-0-3190"
msgid "Crafting Motif 21: Ancient Orc Swords"
msgstr ""

